# Digital Loyalty Card App — Implementation Plan

> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.

**Goal:** Build a B2B2C digital loyalty platform with mobile app (consumer) + web dashboard (merchant) + Supabase backend.

**Architecture:** Turborepo monorepo with Expo SDK 54 (React Native) mobile app, Next.js 15 merchant dashboard, and Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Edge Functions + Realtime) as the backend. QR code + NFC validation, push notifications, Stripe subscriptions.

**Tech Stack:** Expo SDK 54, React Native, Expo Router, Zustand, Next.js 15, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Supabase, Stripe, PostHog, i18next

**Design Doc:** `docs/plans/2026-02-25-loyalty-card-app-design.md`

